http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/andhra-pradesh/Care-dialysis-centre-inaugurated/article14001018.ece

PES Institute of Medical Sciences and Research (PESIMSR), in association with DaVita Care India Pvt. Ltd., opened a world-class dialysis unit at Kuppam, here on Thursday. The DaVita Care centre will feature 15 dialysis machines for maintenance haemodialysis procedures with a provision for another seven for acute and emergency dialysis care. The monthly ‘Patient Scorecards’ given to all patients, will track success across vital parameters such as access, adequacy, anaemia management, haemoglobin and bone management, among others.